Added a standalone Relaxation/Meditation domain that is completely separate from cognitive training. Backend: new RelaxationSession model and schema for logging meditation sessions (duration, completion), with POST and GET endpoints on the existing /api/relaxation router. Frontend: new Relaxation page with guided breathing exercise featuring configurable duration (1/3/5/10 min), animated breathing circle (inhale/exhale), countdown timer, progress bar, and completion summary. Navigation updated in both BottomNav and Sidebar with a 'Wind' icon linking to /relaxation. Route added to App.jsx. Pure utility functions (formatTime, calculateCompletionPercent) exported for testability. All styling uses design system tokens exclusively. No integration with session planner, brain health score, or adaptive difficulty.